DAILY.text:
DUMP -
       COMPRESS                                                       -
       DATASET(                                                       -
               INCLUDE(AKLEIN.**,                                     -
                       AND*.**,                                       -
                      )                                               -
               EXCLUDE( -
                       *.D0*.T*.P*,  /* ZA DUMP DATASETS */           -
                       *.D1*.T*.P*,                                   -
                       *.D2*.T*.P*,                                   -
                       *.D3*.T*.P*,                                   -
                       *.SPFTEMP*.CNTL,                               -
                       *.ISPF.ISPPROF,                                -
                       *.SPFLOG*.LIST,                                -
                      ) -
               BY((DSORG EQ (SAM,PDS,PDSE,VSAM)) (DSCHA EQ 1))        -
              )         -
       RESET OPTIMIZE(4)   OUTDDNAME(DUMP) TOL(ENQF)

MCHANGE.text:
ISREDIT MACRO PROCESS
ISPEXEC VGET FROM
ISPEXEC VGET TO
ISREDIT CHANGE &FROM &TO  ALL
ISREDIT SAVE
ISREDIT END
RETURN
EXIT

SPUFIDYN.text:
SELECT * FROM MVSDSSN.DSSDATASETS A
 WHERE ( A.DATASET LIKE 'OMVS.%.KAR%' )
AND
(
A.KEY =  (
SELECT MAX(B.KEY)
FROM MVSDSSN.DSSDATASETS B
WHERE A.DATASET = B.DATASET )
)
ORDER BY A.DATASET;
